0vw, 2000px" /></p><p><a href="https://www.nme.com/artists/russell-brand">拉塞尔·布兰德</a>透露，他正在接受洗礼，以“把过去抛在脑后”。</p><p>去年，第四频道、 <em>《</em><em>泰晤士报》</em>和<em>《星期日泰晤士报》</em>联合调查，这位喜剧演员被<a href="https://www.nme.com/news/film/russell-brand-accused-of-rape-sexual-assault-and-emotional-abuse-3498938">指控在 2006 年至 2013 年期间犯有多项强奸、袭击和精神虐待罪</a>。这位明星强烈否认所有指控。</p><p>布兰德上周在 Instagram 上分享的一篇帖子中证实，他正在“冒险”并“接受洗礼”。</p><p> “他们向我解释的是，这是一个死亡和重生的机会，”他说。 “这是一个抛开过去并以基督的名义重生的机会。就像加拉太书中所说：你可以作为一个开明和觉醒的人生活。” </p><blockquote class="instagram-media" data-instgrm-captioned data-instgrm-permalink="https://www.instagram.com/reel/C6OD56TKn3x/?utm_source=ig_embed&amp;utm_campaign=loading" data-instgrm-version="14" style=" background:#FFF; border:0; border-radius:3px; box-shadow:0 0 1px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.5),0 1px 10px 0 rgba(0,0,0,0.15); margin: 1px; max-width:658px; min-width:326px; padding:0; width:99.375%; width:-webkit-calc(100% - 2px); width:calc(100% - 2px);"><div style="padding:16px;"><div style="background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 50%; flex-grow: 0; height: 40px; margin-right: 14px; width: 40px;"></div><div style="display: flex; flex-direction: column; flex-grow: 1; justify-content: center;"><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; margin-bottom: 6px; width: 100px;"></div><div style=" background-color: #F4F4F4; border-radius: 4px; flex-grow: 0; height: 14px; width: 60px;"></div></div></div><div style="padding: 19% 0;"></div><div style="display:block; height:50px; margin:0 auto 12px; width:50px;"><svg width="50px" height="50px" viewBox="0 0 60 60" version="1.1" xmlns="https://www.w3.org/2000/svg" xmlns:xlink="https://www.w3.org/1999/xlink"><g stroke="none" stroke-width="1" fill="none" fill-rule="evenodd"><g transform="translate(-511.000000, -20.000000)" fill="#000000"><g><path d="M556.869,30.41 C554.814,30.41 553.148,32.076 553.148,34.131 C553.148,36.186 554.814,37.852 556.869,37.852 C558.924,37.852 560.59,36.186 560.59,34.131 C560.59,32.076 558.924